AFAIK, the sprite glitches were fixed for good. I bought one of the early carts and indeed there were sprite issues, but after modding it I have never seen such problems again. The current carts already come with the fix, and I have never heard of anyone complaining about sprite corruption.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Fri Jun 17, 2011 7:20 pm</p><hr />
